OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779719229
OL,3,CMan attacked after heard speaking
OL,4,CHebrew 'thought he was going to be
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,FA Jewish man attacked in Golders Green
OL,8,Fafter he was heard speaking Hebrew has
OL,9,Ftold ITV News London he thought he was
OL,10,Fgoing to be killed.
OL,12,FThe 22-year-old, who was visiting from
OL,13,FIsrael, was assaulted by a group of
OL,14,Fmasked men early on Monday morning and
OL,15,Fleft with cuts and bruises to his face
OL,16,Fand back.
OL,18,FHis injuries were so bad he had to be
OL,19,Ftreated in hospital.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
