FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779719229
OL,3,CMan attacked after heard speaking
OL,4,CHebrew 'thought he was going to be
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,FSpeaking anonymously he said
OL,8,Fantisemitism would not stop him coming
OL,9,Fto London.
OL,11,F"I think I'm a strong person... I felt
OL,12,Ffor a few seconds, maybe they (are)
OL,13,Fgoing to kill me... if they have a
OL,14,Fknife, why not," he said.
OL,16,F"Something big need to change in
OL,17,FEurope. Not just in London, in Europe.
OL,18,FBecause it cannot continue like that.
OL,26,@tD@_pmtD@cpn
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
