FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779719229
OL,3,CMan attacked after heard speaking
OL,4,CHebrew 'thought he was going to be
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,F"I'm going to come back (to London)...
OL,8,Fbut it's traumatic, I'm in shock now,
OL,9,Fbut I'm going to be careful," he
OL,10,Fexplained.
OL,12,FThe attack took place around 2am on
OL,13,FMonday morning and police were alerted
OL,14,Fby a neighbour who heard what was
OL,15,Fgoing on.
OL,17,FThe victim was dragged across the road
OL,18,Fand his clothes were torn but the
OL,19,Fsuspects fled before officers arrived.
OL,26,@oD@YpmoD@cpn
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
