CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779719229
OL,3,CMan attacked after heard speaking
OL,4,CHebrew 'thought he was going to be
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,FDescribing the attack he said: "They
OL,8,Fkicked me and took me down to the
OL,9,Ffloor and I could not do anything.
OL,11,F"I just closed my eyes and defended
OL,12,Fmyself. They didn't stop.
OL,14,F"They said something very negative in
OL,15,Fanother language."
OL,17,FHe said he was certain he was attacked
OL,18,Fbecause he was speaking Hebrew.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
