OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FPolice said they were still
OL,13,Finvestigating the attack, adding:
OL,14,F"Police were called at 02:05hrs on
OL,15,FMonday, 18 May, following reports that
OL,16,Fa Jewish man had been assaulted by a
OL,17,Fnumber of men outside a property on
OL,18,FThe Grove, NW11.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
