FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779719229
OL,3,CMan attacked after heard speaking
OL,4,CHebrew 'thought he was going to be
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,F"Officers attended within six minutes
OL,8,Fand spoke to the victim, a man in his
OL,9,F20s, who later attended hospital with
OL,10,Finjuries to his face and back.
OL,12,F"The assault is being treated as an
OL,13,Fantisemitic hate crime. No arrests
OL,14,Fhave been made at this stage and
OL,15,Fpolice enquiries continue."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
