OL,3,CMan attacked after heard speaking
OL,4,CHebrew 'thought he was going to be
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,FSpeaking shortly after the attack the
OL,8,FCampaign Against Antisemitism said:
OL,9,F"We cannot wait any longer for real
OL,10,Fintervention against this horrific
OL,11,Fwave of violence against Britain's
OL,12,FJews. We are in dire need of urgent
OL,13,Faction."
